{"id":2667,"date":"2022-10-14T11:40:43","date_gmt":"2022-10-14T09:40:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/?page_id=2667"},"modified":"2023-02-14T14:14:00","modified_gmt":"2023-02-14T13:14:00","slug":"triple-international-conference-2023","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/past-events\/triple-international-conference-2023\/","title":{"rendered":"TRIPLE Conference 2023"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2812\" width=\"1215\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1536x864.png 1536w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1215px) 100vw, 1215px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">On behalf of the Triple Project, we welcome all Open Science enthusiasts to the Final Triple Conference on improving&nbsp;Discovery and Collaboration in Open Science&nbsp;in the previous German capital city Bonn, on&nbsp;1-3 February 2023.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">We are very excited to see the GoTriple project finding flesh and bone; please come and enjoy the research and report your results! We look forward to learning the latest updates from top open science researchers on essential topics, and everything else is presented. The backdrop of the beautiful and historic city of Bonn will add to the pleasure of the meeting and provide lasting memories beyond the science.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">The final TRIPLE Conference will be a hybrid event. Presenters are strongly encouraged to be present in person. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">While the registration for on-site attendance is closed, <strong>registration<\/strong> for <strong>online participation<\/strong> is available for everyone. Once you have submitted your registration, you will get a confirmation email.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a look at the programme here: <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/events\/triple-international-conference-2023\/the-conference-program\/\">https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/events\/triple-international-conference-2023\/the-conference-program\/<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">Please register here: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/triple2023.sciencesconf.org\/registration\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/triple2023.sciencesconf.org\/registration<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When posting about the conference on social media, please use the hashtag #TRIPLE2023.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">The conference will start on the 1st of February at noon and end on the 3rd February at noon. For more travel information and information on the venue please visit: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/events\/travel-information\/\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/events\/travel-information\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\">Looking forward to seeing you soon in Bonn, Germany!<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>On behalf of the Triple Project, we welcome all Open Science enthusiasts to the Final Triple Conference on improving&nb